'''Mulch mold''' was a type of black [[Fungus/Legends|fungus]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Neimoidia/Legends|Neimoidia]]. When marinated in the secretions of the [[Blight beetle/Legends|blight beetle]] once its spores were developed, it was considered a delicacy by the [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidians]]. It was the favorite dish of [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]].

